<br /><h2>Security</h2>Long text which isn&#039;t naturally breakable into lines is forced into pieces.<br /><br />JavaScript script tags, onX handlers and URLs will all be filtered/blocked. Don&#039;t use them unless you want the staff to be alerted to a suspected hacking attempt!<br /><br /><h2>Links</h2>
