<br /><h2>Boxes</h2>You can put things in boxes. For example:<br />[code param="Comcode"][box="My Box"]Testing boxes[/box][/code]&hellip;produces:<br />[box param="My Box"]Testing boxes[/box]<h2>Formatting</h2>
